name: Ekeko #01 (a lot of wishes)
description: The Ekeko, ancient and powerful amulet Tradition says that only his intense smoking habit managed to keep him awake during the long hours that required him to gather his great fortune. And that if you hang a wish on him and offer him a cigar, sooner rather than later he will fulfill your wish Its power level rises when it is given to you, but if you are given an Ekeko you have the obligation to get another copy to give away
